Geez, MusTangTwoForThreeBlankets, <br><br>
I wish I got put in the PonyTurdScoopDetail. At least you get to scoop it up after and use it for fertilizer.<br><br>
I got put in the PossumToedSnoopDetachment. I get to hunker in the bush at night with my scope looking for those Tennessee boys poaching lunch. Caught one a few nights ago. Tripped the claymores and everything! Said his name was Tom, out to take a leak behind the barn, and just got lost. He had such and honest face under his straw hat, I let him go. Those sandles he was wearing though, just not the latest fashion statement.<br><br>
Hey, I kind of like those blankets. I got a real shrunken head hear to trade. It would look good stuck on a pole over by where you bed your ponies. They say it would scare away anything. Even Bot Flies and Evil Spirits and your Mother-in-law.<br><br>
How about one shrunken head for one blanket. That's a great deal! I need a blanket, anyway. Gets down right chilly out here at night. I know you'd really like *this* shrunken head.<br><br>
